data.description: Better than new with all new carpet and paint !! ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 3 % INTEREST RATE!!! Experience comfort and style at 1304 Karen Court in Griffin Park, Hinesville, GA. This 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home offers 2785 sq ft of living space, including a 2-car garage and a fenced-in backyard with vinyl fencing. Inside, you'll find a formal dining room, an open floor plan connecting the living room, kitchen, and breakfast area, and a convenient half bathroom. The kitchen features granite countertops, a kitchen island, stainless steel appliances, and a walk-in pantry. Just renovated with all new paint and flooring throughout, this home offers a fresh and modern aesthetic. Upstairs, there's a laundry room, two bedrooms sharing a Jack and Jill bathroom with private vanities attached to each room, another bedroom with its own private bathroom, and a spacious Owner's Suite with 2 walk-in closets and a private bathroom featuring dual sinks, a stand-up shower, and a garden bathtub. All bedrooms offer walk-in closets for ample storage. The community amenities include two pools and a playground, adding to the appeal of this fantastic home. Just 15 minutes from Fort Stewart, this home combines convenience and style.
